---
title: compute_cells_and_kzg_proofs_polynomialcoeff (fulu-polynomial-commitments-sampling)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_iter : cells = [], proofs = []
    q_iter --> q_coset : for i in range(CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB)
    q_coset --> q_proof : coset = coset_for_cell(CellIndex(i))
    q_proof --> q_append : proof, ys = compute_kzg_proof_multi_impl(poly_coeff, coset)
    q_append --> q_append_proof : cells.append(coset_evals_to_cell(ys))
    q_append_proof --> q_iter : proofs.append(proof)
    q_iter --> q_return : all cells and proofs computed
    q_return --> [*] : return cells, proofs

    note right of q_iter
        INV: Output contains CELLS_PER_EXT_BLOB cells and proofs
        INV: Each proof is valid for its corresponding cell and coset
        INV: O(n^2) complexity; FK20 algorithm preferred for production
    end note
